<i>adverb</i>: 엄숙히 [엄수키], 듬직이 [듬지기] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄숙히 [엄수키]</dt><br>
<dd>1. solemnly; gravely; seriously</dd><br>
<dd>의식이나 분위기 등이 무겁고 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of a ceremony, atmosphere, etc., being heavy and quiet.</dd><br>
<dd>2. solemnly; gravely; seriously</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 태도 등이 무겁고 점잖게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of a speech, attitude, etc., being heavy and refined.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>듬직이 [듬지기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. reliably</dd><br>
<dd>모습이나 성격이 점잖고 믿음직하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that one's behavior or personality looks dependable and decent.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gravely; imposingly</dd><br>
<dd>사물의 겉모양이 크고 당당하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the outward look of an object is big and imposing.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>